Description: The `heckmanGE` package provides tools for the estimation of Heckman 
  selection models with robust variance-covariance matrices. It includes functions 
  for computing the bread and meat matrices, as well as clustered standard errors 
  for generalized Heckman models. The package also offers cluster-robust inference 
  with sandwich estimators, and tools for handling issues related to eigenvalues 
  in covariance matrices.
